author: ETA PRIME
description:
ASUS and Kojima Productions just teamed up for a special edition ROG Flow Z13 (KJP version) — and if you’ve been watching the channel, you already know the Flow Z13 has been one of my favorite devices. This one keeps the same monster platform: AMD Ryzen AI Max+ 395 paired with Radeon 8060S (40 CUs) and quad-channel unified memory up to 128GB LPDDR5X — but the whole device gets that signature Kojima flair with a gold finish + carbon fiber accents that really stands out.

LEARN MORE HERE: https://rog.asus.com/us/
